<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><span style="font-size:90%;"><strong>&#171; <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/salt-the-slug-sheepdog">Previous Tale</a> | <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/maim-the-sky-slay-the-sun-hub">Maim the Sky, Slay the Sun</a> | <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/twenty-step-death-march-to-ultrahell">Next Tale</a> &#187;</strong></span></p>
